General.Name: Fragbite Group AB
General.Description: Fragbite Group AB (publ) operates as a digital gaming entertainment company in the Nordic region. It develops, publishes, distributes, and markets mobile games through its game development studios, including Lucky Kat, FunRock Development, and Prey Studios; and arranges and broadcasts e-sports tournaments live. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden. Fragbite Group AB was a former subsidiary of FunRock Media AB.
